{"tid":1932792,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論下週休刊]ONEPIECE 海賊王 ワンピース 975錦衛門的妙計情報,圖","createTime":"2020-03-19T02:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:35:19.000Z","uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"97c592e4fd20909b2ccfb05736541948316190d9","tid":1932792,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dq7bFtQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDq7bFtQ.jpg&h=a5a78f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1z8eDfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1z8eDfw.jpg&h=ced7b645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n975 錦えもんの一計<br />\n<br />\nサニー号の帆の修繕に手間取って遅れたがかけつけたルフィ達<br />\n<br />\nルフィ、ロー、キッドは暴れまくる<br />\n<br />\nそんな中で現れた狂死郎も自分が傳ジローであることを明かし<br />\n子分達やオロチの信頼を得たことで牢屋敷から解放した侍達と共に助太刀に<br />\n<br />\nそして沈められたと思っていた軍勢達も無事で壊された船は必要なかった船だけだった<br />\n<br />\nその理由を傳ジローは康イエの判じ絵を内通者が傍にいることを察した錦えもんがわざと読み違いをしたからだと思っていたが<br />\n錦えもんは普通に間違えただけだった"},{"pid":"d9fe457897b0b991942ee5cd023e952d50b8becd","tid":1932792,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:46:37.000Z","msg":"日文。。。。。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07df3debc7e2a5b6a7e2a234ede2186d96e5b79","tid":1932792,"uid":50601,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:46:52.000Z","msg":"有冇泰文版呀屌你老母死垃圾 日文點睇呀"},{"pid":"403bcdd879d09c11c80c65b907a5cfcd7398cf8b","tid":1932792,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"你無心貼就唔好搶鳩住啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7176007f3c8e9bef632be75cb013f5064769d62","tid":1932792,"uid":39796,"lik